    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I&#8217;m running out to get some PEARS to bake today! TANKS</>Barbara Kafka has an easy one for 6 poached pears. You just scoop out the innards and stick some cinnamon, cloves inside + lemon juice and lemon/orange zest on the outside of the peeled pear.</>In 8 minutes= et voila! The pear&#8217;s veryown sugar sweetens this dish.</p>
